'''瓦利亚·哈姆扎博士'''是一位印度-巴西科学家，<ref>{{cite web|title= Amazon has a twin river that flows 4.000 metres below the ground|publisher= Mercopress|year= 2011|url= http://en.mercopress.com/2011/08/26/amazon-has-a-twin-river-that-flows-4.000-metres-below-the-ground|accessdate= 2 September 2011|archive-date= 2019-03-01|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190301034211/http://en.mercopress.com/2011/08/26/amazon-has-a-twin-river-that-flows-4.000-metres-below-the-ground|dead-url= no}}</ref>以与伊利莎白·皮门特尔<ref>{{cite web |title= Large Underground River Flowing Beneath The Amazon Rain Forest |publisher= Geeky Gadgets |year= 2011 |url= http://www.geeky-gadgets.com/large-underground-river-flowing-beneath-the-amazon-rain-forest-31-08-2011/ |accessdate= 31 August 2011 |archive-date= 2016-03-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160306122635/http://www.geeky-gadgets.com/large-underground-river-flowing-beneath-the-amazon-rain-forest-31-08-2011/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>共同发现[[哈姆扎河|哈姆扎河]]而闻名，它是位于[[亚马逊河|亚马逊河]]之下的暗河。<ref>{{cite web |title= Underground river 'Rio Hamza' discovered 4km beneath the Amazon |publisher= The Guardian |year= 2011 |url= http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/aug/26/underground-river-amazon |accessdate= 31 August 2011 |archive-date= 2013-06-29 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130629062025/http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/aug/26/underground-river-amazon |dead-url= no }}</ref>哈姆扎是巴西国家天文台地球物理专业常驻教授之一。<ref>{{cite web |title= Professors and Collaborators are displayed following CAPES’ advices as well as determinations of the Technical and Scientific Council of the Observatório Nacional |publisher= Observatório Nacional |year= 2011 |url= http://www.on.br/conteudo/dppg_e_iniciacao/dppg/neweb_geo/conteudo_ingles/docentesingles.html |accessdate= 31 August 2011 |archive-date= 2019-02-17 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190217223240/http://www.on.br/conteudo/dppg_e_iniciacao/dppg/neweb_geo/conteudo_ingles/docentesingles.html |dead-url= n